Just sharing a simple layer system I’ve been building (inspired by Mosaic Builder).

I managed to recreate an outline → layers panel with:

drag-to-reorder + copy
synced hover state both ways
(hover in editor ↔ highlight in layers, and vice versa)

Right now it’s a bit hacky though. When hovering a layer item, I look up the matching [data-puck-component] inside the preview iframe and fire synthetic mouseover/mouseout events to trigger Puck’s native overlay.

Works, but feels like a workaround. Would be great if Puck exposed hover state in core in the future.